eTargeting.model
Class SubscribersModel

java.lang.Object
  eTargeting.model.SubscribersModel

public class SubscribersModel
extends java.lang.Object

The SubscribersModel class represents a list of subscribers and allows the user to create new subscribers.

A subscriber is represented by the following information:

  • A unique ID.
  • A first name.
  • A last name.
  • An email address.
  • An age.
  • A gender.

Version:

Author:
